==Tarakalt==

Isiwan zgan-d deg wetrim (umalu) n tmurt n [[Maṣer]], teqrib tilisa af [[Libya]] yerna teggug (tebɛed) azal n 560 km seg [[Taqahirt]]. D amda i-d yezgan deg ugafa akkw di Maṣer di [[Tidiklet n Qeṭṭara|tidikelt n Qeṭṭara]]. Deg ugafa, ar 300 km, illa usagen n [[Merṣa Maṭruḥ]] af yiri n [[Ilel Agrakal|Yilel Agrakal]]. 


